com.shopgun.android.sdk.api

Class Parameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopgun.android.sdk.api.Parameters
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Api.Param

    public class Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains sub-set of strings, that ShopGun API v2 uses as parameters, for queries to the API.
